TestResource.Description: Executes a SOAP action based on a schema or imported SOAP file.

ActivityConstraintBase.Description: To run the SOAP Request step, provide a value for the EndpointAddress field in the Property Sheet.
To run the SOAP Request step, provide a value for the SoapAction field in the Property Sheet.
To run the SOAP Request step, provide a value for the ContentType field in the Property Sheet.
